Visit this link to see a project that I created about determining suitable wolverine habitat in Colorado through a GIS suitability analysis.
Some things that I learned in this project are:

Curating sources of relevant data across topography, snowpack patterns, and transportation maps;
Developing an ArcGIS model to perform suitability analysis and analyze results;
Communicating results through an Arc StoryMap medium.

